{"tid":2495062,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"據報美國政府將公布對台軍售  為M109A6自走砲","createTime":"2021-04-19T03:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T10:36:17.000Z","uid":125168,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"05a41633d95173a52b6ac4f799ca50387b46402f","tid":2495062,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"報道指拜登政府將公布上任後首份對台軍售案<br />\n<br />\n發佈時間 2021-04-19 10:04<br />\n<br />\n美國據報將會落實向台灣出售M109A6自走砲，是總統拜登上任以來首份對台軍售案。台灣《聯合報》引述消息指，美國在台協會台北辧事處上月知會台方，美國國防安全合作局會在短期內知會國會，向台灣出售M109A6自走砲；台灣會於2023年至2025年分批接收，並由今年起執行附屬設施整建等前期準備工作。台灣的國防部長邱國正表示，一直與美方進行商討，目前沒有接獲正式告知。<br />\n<br />\nM109A6自走砲是美國砲兵部隊的主力砲，內部加裝了防彈設施及半自動彈藥補充系統，同時配備自動射擊管制系統、全球定位以及單頻地空無線電系統，可以在接到指令後一分鐘內發炮，軍方形容能造出「1輛車能打出1個砲兵連的效果」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/news/amp/china/2387816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fchina%2F2387816&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=5f8803b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.881903.com/news/amp/china/2387816</a>"},{"pid":"d72c849f6c149ce6bc52efeb563159c416f24a3b","tid":2495062,"uid":292987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3114caff88189b6f9dc334871cef52c1445faf","tid":2495062,"uid":171094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95fae0d3daef232dda44ccff0e2ab67a27d1d151","tid":2495062,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T03:31:30.000Z","msg":"共諜：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif